Lightweight wrapper for threads/mutexes/condition
variables.

Has been tested on the following platforms:
* PC (UNIX/Windows)
* PlayStation3
* Xbox 1
* Xbox 360
* Gamecube
* Wii
* Android
* iOS
* MacOSX
* Blackberry QNX

Has several implementations:
* OGC LWP Threads (the Gamecube/Wii versions 
uses a pthread wrapper to implement this) 
* Win32 Threads (for Win32/Xbox 1/Xbox 360)
* POSIX Threads
